details.name: Enrage
details.description: Ursa goes into a frenzy, multiplying his Fury Swipes damage and causing him to take 80% less damage. Removes any existing debuffs. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter. DISPEL TYPE: Strong Dispel
details.upgrade_description: Reduces cooldown and allows Ursa to use Enrage while disabled.
